{"tid":163799,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"價值上45億英鎊 探險家找到2戰「黃金沉船」","createTime":"2017-03-20T09:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T16:29:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5280d2c0947c02118faccf4facf42807574e9fd9","tid":163799,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpa64Tv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpa64Tv6.jpg&h=7f32e47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">貝拿勒斯城號（City of Benares）被納粹德軍魚雷擊中沉沒，船上325名乘客罹難，其中還載滿大量黃金。（圖擷取自DailyMail）</span><br />\n2017-03-20  10:06<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕事發於第二次世界大戰前1940年9月，英國一艘滿載戰爭難民的班輪貝拿勒斯城號（City of Benares）被納粹德軍魚雷擊中沉沒，船上325名乘客罹難，船上還載滿大量黃金。經過長達25年的研究，探險家團隊終於找到沉船的位置，估計船上的黃金價值至少45億英鎊（約新台幣1710億元）。<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》報導，黃金在戰爭狀態下是保值貨幣，德國當時為削弱英國的財力，對英國的黃金運輸線路進行嚴密的監控和攻擊，而貝拿勒斯城號就是在其中犧牲。<br />\n探險家團隊經過25年研究後，製作出兩次世界大戰期間英國黃金運輸路徑的數據庫，判斷出大西洋中貝拿勒斯城號的確切位置。據保守估計，船上的黃金價值至少45億英鎊（約新台幣1710億元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009897&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=3d33076a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009897&h=6382af17\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009897</a>"},{"pid":"da4b7ceaf89552336b1528925d9038f078257424","tid":163799,"uid":9191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"></span>"},{"pid":"f3840514b44992b0e17cbd434dbcb1e143573f84","tid":163799,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a440138edd